Author: desperate_housecat
Text: I know it feels like a failure, but 500-700 is still very low, and if it's more than normal then I'm sure your body appreciates the fuel you've been giving it. You are absolutely still at a deficit, and you're probably getting some extra nutrition that your body was craving. And you're not a failure- there's no failing at an ED, just like we all know there's no winning. There's just doing your best to take care of yourself, which I hope you can do for yourself now ‚ù§
